name: FCameraLensSettings
doc: #note, this struct has a details customization in CameraLensSettingsCustomization.cpp/h

MinFocalLength: Minimum focal length for this lens
MaxFocalLength: Maximum focal length for this lens
MinFStop: Minimum aperture for this lens (e.g. 2.8 for an f/2.8 lens)
MaxFStop: Maximum aperture for this lens (e.g. 2.8 for an f/2.8 lens)
MinimumFocusDistance: Shortest distance this lens can focus on.
